flowchart TD
  B0[Supplier bill recorded]
  L0{Linked to approved request - if applicable}
  M0{Match outcome}
  R0{Readiness decision}
  Q0[Handoff to Payments Queue - execution workspace]
  X0[Executed or paid - cash truth owned by Payments Queue]

  B0 --> L0
  L0 -->|Unlinked| M0
  L0 -->|Linked| M0

  M0 -->|Matched| R0
  M0 -->|Mismatch| R0

  R0 -->|Blocked - explicit reason| B0
  R0 -->|Ready for Payment| Q0 --> X0

  subgraph Guardrails[Guardrails]
    G1[Readiness is formed in Spend module]
    G2[Execution state is owned by Payments Queue]
    G3[Unlinked bills default to Blocked in v1]
  end

  R0 -.-> G1
  Q0 -.-> G2
  L0 -.-> G3
